{"questionId":"32992382","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>After deciding that the trout population would increase too quickly, the lake owner proposes instead to remove 750 trout at the end of each year.</p>\n<p>The relationship between <em>D</em><sub>n</sub>, the predicted number of trout at the start of year <em>n</em>, and <em>D</em><sub>n + 1</sub>, the predicted number of trout at the start of year <em>n + 1</em>, is now given by <em>D</em><sub>n + 1</sub> = 1.1<em>D</em><sub>n</sub> - 750 and <em>D</em><sub>1</sub> = 6000.</p>\n<p>It is also known that <em>D</em><sub>n</sub> = -1500(1.1)<sup>n - 1</sup> + 7500.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Show that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>150</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>attempts to use the explicit formula for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></math> to find an expression for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>7500</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>7500</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>7500</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1<br><br></strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1650</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8250</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>7500</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1<br><br></strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>-</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mi>n</mi></msup></math></strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; A1<br><br></strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>150</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em>AG</em></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>attempts to express&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></math> in terms of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><em>(M1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong><em>(A1)</em></strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1500</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>7500</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mfenced><mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>150</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>750</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>750</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>-</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>n</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>150</mn><msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AG</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"32992382","referenceCode":"24N.3.AHL.TZ0.1di","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Show that Dn+1-Dn=-1501.1n-1.","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.6—Simple proof"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":3}
